FIGURE 7.

Leptopareia borneana
(Cameron)

, ♀, lectotype. 
A.
Habitus, lateral view; 
B.
Head, frontal view; 
C.
Head and mesosoma, dorsal view; 
D.
Metasoma, dorsal view; 
E.
Head, dorsal view; 
